title.rendered: SQULPT celebrates Naturals® Week August 14, 2023 – August 20, 2023

content.rendered:
Learn more about their safter and gentler advanced breast augmentation
procedure at @squlpt

AGOURA HILLS, CALIFORNIA, UNITED STATES, August 16, 2023/EINPresswire.com/ — August 14, 2023 – August 20, 2023

Learn more about their safter and gentler advanced breast augmentation
procedure at @squlpt

Celebrate SQULPT advanced softer and gentler breast augmentation procedure, Naturals®, performed exclusively at their newly updated and expanded Agora Hills, CA surgery center during Naturals® Week, Monday, August 14 – Sunday, August 20.

During Naturals® Week SQULPT (@squlpt and YouTube) will provide meaningful content with a series of educational and inspirational videos of the silicone free procedure that does not require general anesthesia or implants, and is absent of excessive scars, all done by gently transferring your own body fat into the breasts.

Along with week-long video testimonials from SQULPT’S thrilled patients, including motivating before and after photos, and Instagram Live interviews with SQULPT’s Top Docs culminates in an exciting breast augmentation give-away (winner announced Monday, September 4, 2023). Learn more at @squlpt and at www.squlptbody.com.

Developed by Dr. Daniel Suissa, MD FRCS, Naturals® is a SQULPT exclusive, using a medically advanced method of preparing and transferring fat to the breasts using their awake lipo-shaping technology: SoftSqulpt®. This is done using miniaturized, gentle vibrations combined with SQULPT’s proprietary blend of calming medicines, transforming the body, pain free, while awake. *Patients can receive more information on the Naturals® procedure by scheduling a virtual consultation at www.squlptbody.com; Naturals® pricing begins at $16,000.

Please visit www.squlptbody.com for more information on the SQULPT way. @squlpt.

For additional information on Naturals® Week at SQULPT, please contact
Kerry Kane at kkane@squlptbody.com.
About SQULPT: SQULPT’s mission is to make every body contouring transformation as safe and natural as possible.

SoftSqulpt® is SQULPT’s patented 360° awake lipo and fat transfer innovation that is safe and gentle and close to pain – free. This modernized approach uses the patients own body fat to enhance the body in an all-natural look with lasting results. No silicone, no general anesthesia and very little downtime. In addition to SoftSqulpt®, SQULPT is also the innovator behind the Petite BBL, XL BBL®, Naturals ® (breast augmentation) and the Silicone Free Zone®. Other body shaping areas include thighs and legs, arms, mid-section, the chin, and neck.

SQULPT currently has an office in the Los Angeles area and will be opening a surgery center in Miami, FL later in 2023.

Kerry Kane
Squlpt Body
